Private Equity Recruitment
-
Abu Dhabi
Our client is one of the largest principal investment teams in the Middle East, with a significant amount of capital under management, strong dealflow and flexible sector coverage. They are looking for an SVP / Associate Director to join their team, based full time in the Middle East, to focus on oil and gas investments. The team has a global investment remit.
RESPONSIBILITIES:
You will be responsible for all elements of the deal execution process from screening to execution You will be expected to run entire deal processes with minimal supervision – this will also include managing junior resources within the team
SKILLS WE’RE LOOKING FOR:
Significant experience in private equity in the oil and gas sector is required Candidates must have significant understanding of the entire M&A; process Must have experience of creating and managing due diligence projects and of leading negotiations with counterparties
Recruiters Reference: 4290 /2D
